185
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:36,708
No, look, Albert. He's not my Àlex,
and that's not the point.

186
00:08:36,791 --> 00:08:38,500
Why didn't you tell me
you were in trouble?

187
00:08:38,583 --> 00:08:39,541
