190
00:08:44,625 --> 00:08:46,625
[melancholy music plays]

191
00:08:50,625 --> 00:08:52,708
-Appetizer?
-[both] No, thanks.

192
00:08:53,208 --> 00:08:54,375
-Wanna sit?
-Oh yeah.

193
00:08:55,166 --> 00:08:57,875
