574
00:27:23,833 --> 00:27:27,166
-Five minutes left till midnight!
-[crowd cheers]

575
00:27:29,166 --> 00:27:31,208
I always feel super nervous
till I hear the bells.

576
00:27:31,291 --> 00:27:32,583
[Álex and Ibra chuckle]

